dct_title_s: Map of the City of New York
dct_description_sm: Covers all of Manhattan, New York (N.Y.) south of 119th Street; also the westernmost parts of Queens and Brooklyn, New York (N.Y.) and part of Jersey City and Hoboken (N.J.) Shows existing and proposed streets, railroads, piers.  Date from previously assigned call number.  Relief shown by hachures.
